Interface IReferenceElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IClass, IDataElement, IHasDataSpecification, IHasExtensions, IHasSemantics, IQualifiable, IReferable, ISubmodelElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnhancedReferenceElement, ReferenceElement

    public interface IReferenceElement
extends IDataElement
    A reference element is a data element that defines a logical reference to another element within the same or another AAS or a reference to an external object or entity.
